					<dcterms:bibliographicCitation xml:lang="en">Sloetjes, Hans. 2022. “ELAN.” Version 6.4. Windows/macOS/Linux. [Java application]. Nijmegen: Max Planck Institute for Psycholinguistics, The Language Archive. https://archive.mpi.nl/tla/elan.</dcterms:bibliographicCitation>
